meta_table_content.sql_pattern:
SELECT MAX("LO_ORDERDATE")
FROM "LINEORDER"
INNER JOIN "CUSTOMER" ON "LINEORDER"."LO_CUSTKEY" = "CUSTOMER"."C_CUSTKEY"
INNER JOIN "SUPPLIER" ON "LINEORDER"."LO_SUPPKEY" = "SUPPLIER"."S_SUPPKEY"
LIMIT 1

SELECT "LINEORDER"."LO_ORDERKEY", "LINEORDER"."LO_CUSTKEY", "CUSTOMER"."C_PHONE"
FROM "LINEORDER"
INNER JOIN "CUSTOMER" ON "LINEORDER"."LO_CUSTKEY" = "CUSTOMER"."C_CUSTKEY"
INNER JOIN "SUPPLIER" ON "LINEORDER"."LO_SUPPKEY" = "SUPPLIER"."S_SUPPKEY"
LIMIT 1
